04:19.200 --> 04:22.158
l'm never gonna stop, Alan.
You know me better than that.

04:22.360 --> 04:24.476
Okay, fine. l'll tell you.

04:24.640 --> 04:26.790
First of all, there's no women.

04:26.960 --> 04:30.111
lmaginary. My next guess
was gonna be imaginary.

04:30.840 --> 04:32.796
