-Are you serious?

05:19.280 --> 05:22.238
And by serious l mean dumber
than a bag of doorknobs.

05:22.400 --> 05:24.277
Look, we went out
to dinner weeks ago. . .

05:24.440 --> 05:26.670
. . .to talk about getting Jake
into middle school.

05:26.840 --> 05:29.434
Before you know it, we're laughing,
having a great time.

05:29.600 --> 05:33.639
l can see the humor in trying to get
the little bonehead into a good school.

05:34.720 --> 05:37.234
