dating your ex-wife.

05:37.400 --> 05:40.119
l know what you're thinking.
l'm being naive and romantic.

05:40.280 --> 05:42.475
Not even close.

05:42.680 --> 05:45.717
You can't overlook the fact
that we still have a lot in common.

05:45.880 --> 05:48.394
Yeah, neither of you
have any respect for you.

05:49.400 --> 05:53.473
