another try and so do l.

05:53.640 --> 05:56.598
We can't let Jake know, we don't
want him to get his hopes up.

05:56.800 --> 06:01.555
Oh, buddy, why don't you just take
an electric sander to your testicles?

06:03.640 --> 06:06.074
