10:47.000 --> 10:48.558
Okay. What is it?

10:52.800 --> 10:53.994
Oh, for God's sake.

10:54.160 --> 10:56.549
Wait, there's more.

11:01.200 --> 11:04.988
Twins, Alan. l got them for you,
but you can share if you want.

11:05.160 --> 11:06.832
Charlie, no.

11:07.000 --> 11:08.991
Fine, you can have them both.

11:09.160 --> 11:11.913
Bad luck to split sisters anyway.

11:12.120 --> 11:13.792
l don't want them.
l'm going to Judith's.

11:13.960 --> 11:16.235
