-Are you sure?

11:30.160 --> 11:32.799
Even together, these girls aren't
as old as your ex-wife.

11:32.960 --> 11:34.359
Bye.

11:36.440 --> 11:38.158
Oh, for the love of God.

11:38.760 --> 11:40.796
Stop turning.

11:41.000 --> 11:42.752
Show's over.

11:44.200 --> 11:46.873
-lsn't he adorable?
-Yeah.

11:47.040 --> 11:49.679
