he's like a little angel.

11:56.280 --> 11:58.157
l was planning to have
a glass of wine. . .

11:58.320 --> 12:00.117
. . .sit in the hot tub
before you came.

12:00.280 --> 12:03.317
l'm sorry. l just wanted to be sure
he got the book. l'll get out.

12:03.480 --> 12:05.232
Alan. Would you like to join me?

12:05.400 --> 12:07.550
