of upkeep.

12:46.840 --> 12:52.710
Actually, all wood that's outside
requires upkeep except trees.

12:52.920 --> 12:54.717
They seem to have it down.

12:55.320 --> 12:56.469
Alan, are you nervous?

12:56.680 --> 12:57.829
