15:41.680 --> 15:43.955
lt's too late for you, Charlie.

15:44.160 --> 15:47.118
No, l mean,
what happens to me and Jake?

15:47.280 --> 15:48.679
l'll never get to see him.

15:49.760 --> 15:51.557
You really love the little guy, huh?

15:52.240 --> 15:55.073
Yeah, l guess l do.

15:55.680 --> 15:57.398
Love hurts, Rose.

15:57.600 --> 15:59.750
Yes, it does.

15:59.920 --> 16:01.831
Especially when you've given
your heart. . .

16:02.000 --> 16:04.116
. . .to someone who barely knows
you exist.

16:04.280 --> 16:08.637
