the way you do. . .

16:11.080 --> 16:12.877
. . .leaving you to stand outside. . .

16:13.040 --> 16:14.598
. . .alone in the night. . .

16:14.760 --> 16:18.116
. . .wishing with all your heart
that he would come to his senses. . .

16:18.280 --> 16:23.115
. . .and realize that his true happiness
lies with you and no one else. . .

16:23.280 --> 16:25.874
. . .but knowing all the while
that it will never happen. . .

16:26.040 --> 16:29.749
. . .because he's a selfish, immature,
heartless jerk.

16:33.880 --> 16:35.472
l mean. . .

16:36.240 --> 16:37.275
. . .poor baby.

16:42.320 --> 16:45.073
Okay, l'm gonna stick my neck
out here. . .

16:45.240 --> 16:47.515
. . .and say that was the best sex
we ever had.

16:47.680 --> 16:49.796
-l agree.
-Not that it wasn't good before.

16:49.960 --> 16:51.109
lt wasn't.

16:52.680 --> 16:54.875
Okay, granted.

16:56.840 --> 16:58.478
Which raises the question:

16:59.160 --> 17:00.832
Why is it so much better now?

17:01.000 --> 17:03.116
-Does it matter?
-Well, no, not really.

17:03.280 --> 17:05.156
l mean, just curious.

